    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="975"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d975">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.42/308: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bucknell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-02">December 2,
                            1943</date>.<lb/>[Received December 2—3:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>8409. For Turner. Department’s 7351, November 20. Dia [<hi rend="italic"
                        >India</hi>] has become full member of Conference of Allied Ministers of
                    Education and Dominion Governments have received formal invitation to become
                    full members. New Zealand observer at Conference informed Embassy observer today
                    that New Zealand did not wish to become full member unless the United States did
                    likewise and that no action would be taken until our position is determined.
                    Attitudes of other Dominion observers have not been ascertained but New Zealand
                    observer indicated that other Dominions will also await United States
                    action.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucknell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
